  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sanitary Pads to Keep 600 Young Girls in School</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">For every year a girl stays in school, her future income increases with 10% to 20%. A woman invests 70% of her income in her family. We invest in girls, because investing in girls&apos; means investing in a better future for everyone. We are offering social enterprise opportunities, creating  viable business for young girls training them to produce the Lucky Girl  Sanitary Pads. Distributed in rural schools to support girls to concentrate with their education and create an income stream for them.</narrative>
  </description>
